                <a href="/about">About the game.</a>
                </p>
                
              </div>
              <div class="col l4 offset-l2 s12" style="padding-top: 32px;">
                <ul>
                  <li><a class="footerlink grey-text text-lighten-3" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/alexwolf47/live_view_demo">
